<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>DP on TosakaUCW的博客</title><link>https://TosakaUCw.github.io/tags/dp/</link><description>Recent content in DP on TosakaUCW的博客</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Wed, 23 Sep 2020 19:54:08 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://TosakaUCw.github.io/tags/dp/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Luogu P4329 [COCI2006-2007#1] Bond（状态压缩，DP）</title><link>https://TosakaUCw.github.io/post/luogu_p4329/</link><pubDate>Wed, 23 Sep 2020 19:54:08 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://TosakaUCw.github.io/post/luogu_p4329/</guid><description>&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://www.luogu.com.cn/problem/P4329" target="_blank">题目链接&lt;/a>&lt;/p>
